<!doctype html><html><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1"><title>Ed Hatrick Smith - Radio Hauraki app. project</title><meta name="description" content="Ed Hatrick-Smith: Radio Hauraki project "/><meta name="keywords" content="web developer, desginer, photographer, awesome person, solutions"/><meta name="author" content="Edward Hatrick-Smith: ed.hatricksmith@gmail.com"/><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styles.projects.min.css"/><?php $thisPage="work";?><?php include_once("/home/akolob/public_html/analyticstracking.php") ?></head><body><?php include("/home/akolob/public_html/header.php");?><div id="projects"><h1 class="works_heading">Radio Hauraki app.</h1><p class="breadcrumbs"><em><a href="/work/work.php">Work</a> / Radio Hauraki app.</em></p><article><p class="projects_first">Radio Hauraki is one of New Zealand's longest running radio brands. Being a media provider they are actively modernising their media and advertising platforms. The Hauraki smartphone app. is expected to play an increasingly pivotal role as part of an integrated solution for advertising clients going forward.</p><p>As a <a href="http://theradionetwork.co.nz/" target="_blank">TRN</a> employee I was approached from within the company to develop a design for the Hauraki app., along with several other key TRN brands. I'm a fan of the station so found it relatively fun to produce the mock-up. It was developed by a third party provider in the U.S.</p><p>Unfortunately it appears Hauraki is going through yet another re-brand (3 in 2 years?), so I suspect the app. will be replaced shortly, if they have not already done so.</p></article><section><h2 class="works_heading">Project Images</h2><div id="container" class="project_width"><div id="container" class="project_width"><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/hauraki/image_01_lge.jpg"><div id="project_lg" class="project"><img src="/images/works/projects/hauraki/image_01_sml.jpg" alt="Hauraki detail 01"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/hauraki/image_02_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/hauraki/image_02_sml.jpg" alt="Hauraki splash page"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/hauraki/image_03_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/hauraki/image_03_sml.jpg" alt="Hauraki detail 02"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/hauraki/image_04_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/hauraki/image_04_sml.jpg" alt="Hauraki detail 03"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a></div></section></div><div class="clearfix"></div><?php include("/home/akolob/public_html/footer.php");?><script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js"></script><script src="/js/jquery.projects.min.js" ></script><script type="text/javascript">$(".fancybox") .attr('rel', 'gallery') .fancybox({padding : 0 ,minWidth : 215 ,maxWidth : 900 ,autoSize : true ,maxHeight : 600 ,});</script><script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js"></script><script src="/js/jquery.isotope-min.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">$(function(){var $container=$('#container');$container.isotope({itemSelector: '.project'});});</script></body></html>